content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 186.6 - Delivery to any carrier

State Regulations

Closed packages of apples delivered to a transportation
company for shipment are presumed to be intended for sale, and must be packed
and branded as required by law, unless the owner can prove that such apples are
not intended for sale as packed. Notes
